{
  "texts": [
    "The question is political.It is no mystery that there is a politics to AI [71][72][73].",
    "Contrary to what animistic interpretations of AI might suggest, there is no magic in AI.",
    "What we are witnessing is not a magic show, but rather a game of politics that a Marxian politico-economic perspective can help us comprehend.",
    "In these terms, the AI ethics industry which has been producing a voluminous corpus of ethical guidelines regarding the creation and deployment of AI technology, is not helping us to overcome the impasse discussed in this section.",
    "This is a diverse sector comprising a variety of voices, ranging from international organizations and corporations to business consultancies and independent ethicists [74]."
  ]
}